{"tid":911814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲大學生無Common sense 架咩？","createTime":"2018-11-22T07:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T07:56:23.000Z","uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2c2a20bf8f5af0822633284a46bd9d8229e789","tid":911814,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"上面呢句係我啲長輩家庭whatsapp group今朝老事常出現，唔知大家有無？<br />\n<br />\n今朝訓醒之後我回左<br />\n<br />\n 「常識幫唔到你上大學架! 成績先得架！」<br />\n<br />\n咁有人就答左句，無common sense 出黎點做嘢？<br />\n<br />\n咁我有講笑咁答<br />\n<br />\n「讀浸會，你普通話唔叻，畢業都有困難啦！要Common sense把鬼？」"},{"pid":"1bd36156e6d49a6f5d750acfa2e16d753b9618fa","tid":911814,"uid":220451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"3d4996ab936220762e60e347be8b94b4c2fff13e","tid":911814,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"0/10"}]}